HEADWORD: Thoroughpaced
<hw>Thor"ough*paced`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Perfect in
what is undertaken; complete; going all lengths; <as>as, a
<ex>thoroughplaced</ex> Tory or Whig</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If she be a <qex>thoroughplaced</qex> impostor.</q> <rj><qau>Sir
W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thoroughpin</ent>⟦br⟧
